Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the V2X for automotive market would exhibit a CAGR of 45.9% for the forecast period. Rising demand for efficient safety norms in automobiles and autonomous passenger vehicles on the roads are the two major factors attributable to the growth of V2X for automotive market. In terms of market value, it will stand tall by USD 12,859 million by the year 2028.
